49
00:02:11,640 --> 00:02:13,440
Look at the signboard there.

50
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,320
It's a glasses frame,

51
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:18,160
it says "Sabae."

52
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:21,680
