how you're piling up the glasses.

158
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:20,920
So when pairs of glasses overlap...

159
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:24,920
They fall, as you can see.

160
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:28,360
Also, he can't see ahead,

161
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:30,520
so he can't choose glasses
that are easy to wear.

162
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,600
I see.

163
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:35,040
There is still space on the head
to wear them,

164
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:37,120
but Miyagawa can't see.

165
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,080
I see.

166
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,400
I see.

167
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:42,880
- The last spurt.
- You can do it!

168
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:45,560
Wow, it looks like
they are his eyes.

169
00:07:45,640 --> 00:07:49,280
- Four, three, two, one.
- The lowest part.

170
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:51,160
Stop.

171
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,920
I think I wore many pairs.

172
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:56,440
Wow, he did so well!

173
00:07:57,800 --> 00:08:00,120
Oh, I think I made it, right?

174
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:02,640
Then...

175
00:08:02,760 --> 00:08:03,920
Thank you.

176
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:05,320
Thank you.

177
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:06,640
What's his record?

178
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,760
Thank you.

179
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:09,200
Thank you.

180
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:11,280
Thank you. So...

181
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:13,320
24 pairs.

182
00:08:14,280 --> 00:08:18,800
In fact, the real difficult part of
Megamori starts at the 25th pair.

183
00:08:20,960 --> 00:08:22,160
Stop.

184
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:24,040
The same. 24 pairs.

185
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:26,120
He can't break his record.

186
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:31,760
25 pairs.
It's the barrier of 25 again!

187
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:34,960
This is the winning record so far.

188
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:39,200
The champion hit a big record
of 35 pairs in 2019.

189
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:41,440
Obviously it also depends on luck,

190
00:08:41,560 --> 00:08:44,200
but there's a chance he can win
if he can wear 30 pairs.

191
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:47,280
There's a chance if I wear
as many as 28 pairs.

192
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:49,560
I'll do it like the real thing.

193
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:54,440
Miyagawa improves his concentration.

194
00:08:55,400 --> 00:08:56,240
Okay!

195
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,400
He's fired up!

196
00:08:57,760 --> 00:08:59,280
He aims to wear 28 pairs.

197
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,200
You can do it.

198
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:01,720
Ready, start!

199
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:02,680
Start!

200
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,120
You can do it.

201
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:09,480
He put the glasses on
and leaves no gap.

202
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:10,480
You can do it.

203
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:16,240
Now is the crucial part.

204
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:19,600
How many more pairs of glasses
can he put on top of his head?

205
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:23,440
Miyagawa is grasping the feeling.

206
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:25,800
He looks very focused.

207
00:09:25,880 --> 00:09:27,960
They get trapped by his hair
many times.

208
00:09:28,040 --> 00:09:29,920
The pace he's putting them on at
isn't bad, either.

209
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:32,920
30 seconds left.

210
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:36,800
The sunglasses that might fall
are also fixed in place.

211
00:09:36,880 --> 00:09:38,400
Wow, that was impressive!

212
00:09:38,880 --> 00:09:42,280
He won't go past 25
if he makes any mistake.

213
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:44,840
He isn't thinking.

214
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:46,240
The last spurt.

215
00:09:46,680 --> 00:09:49,600
The glasses are coming apart,
but they manage to stay.

216
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:50,920
Wow, they're trapped!

217
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:51,840
Impressive!

218
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:52,880
10 seconds left.

219
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:55,840
Isn't this really impressive?

220
00:09:56,520 --> 00:09:59,480
- Don't let them fall...
- Don't let them fall!

221
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:02,040
- Amazing!
- Impressive!

222
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,720
- Stop.
- It's over.

223
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:06,680
I think I made it.

224
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:09,040
20.

225
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,840
What is his record?

226
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,960
28!

227
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:15,280
Wow, maybe I can do it!

228
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:18,880
He achieved his goal, 28 pairs.

229
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:22,720
Somehow I really understand now.

230
00:10:22,920 --> 00:10:24,680
I do better in a real match,

231
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:27,080
so I'm confident I can put on
over 30 pairs.

232
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:29,600
What's left
is the Champion's nerves.

233
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:33,800
I'd like the cooperation
of our crew.

234
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:36,560
Please put the camera
very close to his face.

235
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:41,720
And now is the time
for the final battle.

236
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:45,040
I must do it. I'll defeat him.
Call the champion here!

237
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:46,640
Champion twice in a row,

238
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,040
Mr Yamahara!

239
00:10:51,760 --> 00:10:53,800
Megamori's absolute champion,

240
00:10:53,920 --> 00:10:55,880
Hiromori Yamahara.

241
00:10:56,480 --> 00:11:00,040
The way he carries himself
is like a glasses advert.

242
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:02,720
35 pairs in one minute.

243
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:05,440
This man made
an overwhelming world record.

244
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:06,600
He has a nice nose.

245
00:11:06,680 --> 00:11:09,120
Mr Yamahara? Nice to meet you.

246
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:11,840
I just practised for a bit,

247
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:13,240
it's difficult.

248
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,280
It is difficult.

249
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:16,560
I watched a bit. You're good at it.

250
00:11:16,640 --> 00:11:18,160
- Really?
- I'm in trouble.

251
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:19,440
I'm a bit nervous.

252
00:11:19,520 --> 00:11:21,440
- May I challenge you?
- Yes.

253
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:22,960
I'm looking forward to it.

254
00:11:23,880 --> 00:11:25,280
Let's do it, then.

255
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:29,360
Megamori special version starts now.

256
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:34,600
The heated battle between men
in glasses is going to start.

257
00:11:35,040 --> 00:11:36,320
The time limit is one minute.

258
00:11:36,560 --> 00:11:40,760
The one who wears more pairs
of glasses on his face wins.

259
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:44,520
If Miyagawa wins, he'll be given
a pair of golden glasses.

260
00:11:44,880 --> 00:11:48,760
If the champion wins, we'll give him
a happi with Miyagawa's autograph.

261
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:50,720
Mr Miyagawa, are you confident?

262
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,240
To be honest...

263
00:11:58,120 --> 00:11:59,240
